data.description: 100% FINANCING PLUS 5% CLOSING COST FINANCING AVAILABLE ON THIS HOME!    POOL HOME * BRAND NEW ROOF AUGUST 2023 with WARRANTY * CORNER LOT * NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED * NEWER AC STILL UNDER WARRANTY *    This single family home offers the perfect blend of affordability, comfort, and Florida living, located in the heart of Spring Hill. Nestled on a peaceful neighborhood with NO HOA and NO CDD, this spacious home is designed to meet the needs of a first time home buyer, a growing family, a couple seeking retirement tranquility, or anyone looking for a prime Florida residence.    This home boasts 3 bedrooms, with a split floorplan, providing ample space for family members and guests alike. The master suite is located on one side of the home, featuring plenty of room for a king sized bed and plenty of furniture, and an en-suite master bath with a separate tub and shower, while the other 2 bedrooms are on the other side of the home, separated by an extra large living area with cathedral ceilings.    The open-concept design connects the living room and formal dining room, while the kitchen has a huge eat-in kitchen dining area as well, making it ideal for entertaining and creating cherished memories with loved ones. Newer stainless steel dishwasher with stainless interior.    Enjoy the beautiful Florida weather in your private outdoor oasis. Cool off in the pool and enjoy your screened, covered lanai, provide a perfect space for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. Add a fence for privacy or to let your fur babies run and get some exercise.    Conveniently located in Spring Hill, you're just moments away from shopping centers, restaurants, schools and medical. Also, Weeki Wachee Springs, State Park, Linda Pederson Park and Buccaneer Bay Waterpark are only a few miles down the road. The vibrant community and easy access to major highways make this location ideal for both work and play.    This property is ready to welcome you home. Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of Florida paradise. Schedule a showing today and imagine the possibilities!
